#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; is a program for learning to touch type. &i18n-ktouch; "
"provides you with text to train on and adjusts to different levels depending "
"on how good you are. It displays which key to press next and the correct "
"finger to use."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; je program za učenje slepega tipkanja. &i18n-ktouch; vam "
"ponuja besedilo za urjenje in se prilagaja različnim nivojem glede na to, "
"kako dobri ste. Prikaže, katero tipko pritisniti naslednjo in kateri prst "
"uporabiti."

