#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Learning touch typing with &i18n-ktouch;"
msgstr "Učenje slepega tipkanja z &i18n-ktouch;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "What is &i18n-ktouch;?"
msgstr "Kaj je &i18n-ktouch;?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-ktouch; is a program for learning to touch type."
msgstr "&i18n-ktouch; je program za učenje slepega tipkanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; provides you with text to train on and adjusts to different "
"levels depending on how good you are. It shows your keyboard and indicates "
"which key to press next and the correct finger to use."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; vam ponuja besedilo za urjenje in se prilagaja različnim "
"nivojem glede na to, kako dobri ste. Prikazuje vašo tipkovnico in označuje, "
"katero tipko pritisniti naslednjo in kateri prst uporabiti."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The main screen of &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Glavni zaslon &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The main screen of &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Glavni zaslon &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; is a touch typing tutor aimed mostly at personal use. You "
"learn typing with all fingers, step by step, without having to look down at "
"the keyboard all the time to find the right keys which slows you down a lot."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; je učitelj slepega tipkanja, namenjen predvsem osebni uporabi. "
"Naučite se tipkati z vsemi prsti, korak za korakom, ne da bi morali ves čas "
"gledati navzdol na tipkovnico, da bi našli prave tipke, kar vas zelo "
"upočasni."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "Features"
msgstr "Zmožnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In its current version, &i18n-ktouch; has quite a number of features, such "
"as:"
msgstr "V trenutni različici &i18n-ktouch; ima kar nekaj zmožnosti, kot so:"

#. Tag: simpara
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ships with dozens different courses in many languages and a comfortable "
"course editor"
msgstr ""
"Priloženo na desetine različnih tečajev v številnih jezikih in udoben "
"urejevalnik tečajev"

#. Tag: simpara
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Support for different keyboard layouts with the ability to use and edit user-"
"defined layouts"
msgstr ""
"Podpora za različne postavitve tipkovnice z možnostjo uporabe in urejanja "
"uporabniško določenih postavitev"

#. Tag: simpara
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"During your training session &i18n-ktouch; collects comprehensive "
"statistical information to help you or your teacher analyze your progress"
msgstr ""
"Med vadbo &i18n-ktouch; zbira izčrpne statistične podatke, ki vam ali vašemu "
"učitelju pomagajo analizirati vaš napredek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are many more features which will be discussed in the appropriate "
"chapters of this manual."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja veliko več zmožnosti, ki bodo obravnavane v ustreznih poglavjih tega "
"priročnika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "Getting started"
msgstr "Kako začeti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here's another screenshot of &i18n-ktouch; in action, this time with a "
"German keyboard and training lesson:"
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je še en posnetek zaslona &i18n-ktouch; v akciji, tokrat z nemško "
"tipkovnico in lekcijo usposabljanja:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Main screen of &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Glavni zaslon &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Main screen of &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Glavni zaslon &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Even though learning touch typing with &i18n-ktouch; and using the program "
"should be very simple we will look a bit closer at &i18n-ktouch; in the "
"following sections."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav je učenje slepega tipkanja z &i18n-ktouch; in bi morala biti uporaba "
"programa zelo preprosta, si bomo nekoliko podrobneje ogledali &i18n-ktouch; "
"v naslednjih razdelkih."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating your first profile"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje vašega prvega profila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first time you start &i18n-ktouch; it will open a special screen helping "
"you to create your first profile. You can choose the name of your profile "
"and the level of your typing skills."
msgstr ""
"Ko prvič zaženete &i18n-ktouch; se bo odprl poseben zaslon, ki vam bo "
"pomagal ustvariti vaš prvi profil. Izberete lahko ime svojega profila in "
"stopnjo svojih veščin tipkanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The level you choose determines the general operation of &i18n-ktouch;. In "
"beginner mode lessons are unlocked one by one after you pass them, for "
"advanced typist all lessons are available right from the beginning."
msgstr ""
"Raven, ki jo izberete, določa splošno delovanje &i18n-ktouch;. V začetnem "
"načinu se lekcije odklenejo ena za drugo, ko jih opravite, za naprednega "
"strojepisca pa so vse lekcije na voljo od začetka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Think about your choice, you won't able to change the type of a profile "
"later. But you can always create new profiles to revisit this decision."
msgstr ""
"Premislite o izbiri, kasneje ne boste mogli spremeniti vrste profila. Vedno "
"pa lahko ustvarite nove profile, da ponovno premislite o tej odločitvi."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Welcome screen of &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pozdravni zaslon &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Welcome screen of &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pozdravni zaslon &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After pressing <guibutton>Start Training</guibutton> you will be taken to "
"the home screen. This screen will also be the first screen visible when you "
"run &i18n-ktouch; the next time."
msgstr ""
"Ko pritisnete <guibutton>Začni vadbo</guibutton>, boste preusmerjeni na "
"začetni zaslon. Ta zaslon bo tudi prvi viden zaslon, ko zaženete &i18n-"
"ktouch; naslednjič."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "Picking a lesson"
msgstr "Izbira lekcije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The home screen of &i18n-ktouch; consists of a toolbar and the course "
"selector. For more information see <xref linkend=\"training_preparation\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Začetni zaslon &i18n-ktouch; sestoji iz orodne vrstice in izbirnika tečaja. "
"Za več informacij glejte <xref linkend=\"training_preparation\"/>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Home screen of &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Začetni zaslon &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Home screen of &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Začetni zaslon &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; will show you the first course available for your current "
"keyboard layout."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; vam bo pokazal prvi tečaj, ki je na voljo za vašo trenutno "
"razporeditev tipkovnice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can switch between courses or choose <link linkend=\"custom_lessons"
"\">custom lessons</link> by clicking their thumbnails in the right part of "
"the window."
msgstr ""
"Preklapljate lahko med tečaji ali izberete <link linkend=\"custom_lessons"
"\">lekcije po meri</link> tako, da kliknete njihove sličice v desnem delu "
"okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On some platforms, especially on &Microsoft; &Windows;, automatic keyboard "
"layout detection is not available. In that case you have to click on the "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button in the toolbar, "
"select <guisubmenu> Configure Keyboard...</guisubmenu> submenu and choose "
"the name of keyboard layout or some keyboard layout which is similar to "
"yours. If your keyboard is not included, you can define your own keyboard "
"layout yourself, see <xref linkend=\"create_layouts\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Na nekaterih platformah, zlasti na &Microsoft; &Windows; samodejno "
"zaznavanje postavitve tipkovnice ni na voljo. V tem primeru morate v orodni "
"vrstici klikniti gumb <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>, "
"izbrati <guisubmenu> Podmeni Konfiguriraj tipkovnico...</guisubmenu> in "
"izberite ime razporeditve tipkovnice ali kakšno postavitev tipkovnice, ki je "
"podobna vaši. Če vaša tipkovnica ni priložena, lahko sami določite lastno "
"razporeditev tipkovnice, glejte <xref linkend=\"create_layouts\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose your lesson from the list on left of the window. You cannot choose "
"the locked lessons with <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-object-locked.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> as they are too difficult for your current skills. Pass "
"lessons to unlock new ones. The preview of the selected lesson will be shown "
"on the right of lessons list."
msgstr ""
"Na seznamu na levi strani okna izberite svojo lekcijo. Ne morete izbrati "
"zaklenjenih lekcij z <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-object-locked.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>, ker so pretežke za vaše trenutne spretnosti. Prenesite "
"lekcije, da odklenete nove. Predogled izbrane lekcije bo prikazan na desni "
"strani seznama lekcij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More information about the selected course can be shown and hidden again "
"using <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-dialog-"
"information.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"button next to the course title."
msgstr ""
"Več informacij o izbranem tečaju lahko znova prikažete in skrijete z uporabo "
"gumba <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-dialog-"
"information.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> poleg "
"naslov predmeta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you finished with the selection click on <guibutton>Start Training</"
"guibutton> to go to the training &i18n-ktouch; screen."
msgstr ""
"Ko končate z izbiro, kliknite <guibutton>Začni vadbo</guibutton>, da greste "
"na vadbo &i18n-ktouch; zaslon."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Training"
msgstr "Usposabljanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid "The training window of &i18n-ktouch; shows three main sections:"
msgstr "Vadbeno okno &i18n-ktouch; prikazuje tri glavne razdelke:"

#. Tag: simpara
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid "Some typing statistics in info boxes at the top"
msgstr "Nekaj statističnih podatkov o tipkanju v informacijskih poljih na vrhu"

#. Tag: simpara
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid "The text you need to type"
msgstr "Besedilo, ki ga morate natipkati"

#. Tag: simpara
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "The keyboard visualization"
msgstr "Vizualizacija tipkovnice"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The training screen of &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Zaslon za vadbo &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The training screen of &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Zaslon za vadbo &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Visibility of training screen parts can be configured using <link linkend="
"\"configuration_dialog\">&i18n-ktouch; configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Vidnost delov zaslona za usposabljanje je mogoče konfigurirati z <link "
"linkend=\"configuration_dialog\">&i18n-ktouch; konfiguracijskim pogovornim "
"oknom</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Place your two index fingers on the two keys on your keyboard with the two "
"little tactile markers near the center of the middle character row. With "
"that done your other fingers will find their intended keys almost "
"automatically. Your thumbs should rest above the space key, the only key you "
"will ever use them for when touch typing. The other fingers should be placed "
"on the three keys adjacent to the marked keys on the center row. Keys for "
"the same finger are grouped together through their color. Try to move your "
"hands as little as possible and always try to return your fingers to their "
"resting positions after you have typed a character."
msgstr ""
"Kazalca položite na dve tipki na tipkovnici z dvema majhnima otipljivima "
"oznakama blizu sredine srednje vrstice znakov. S tem bodo vaši drugi prsti "
"skoraj samodejno našli želene tipke. Vaši palci naj počivajo nad "
"preslednico, edino tipko, za katero jih boste kdaj uporabljali pri tipkanju "
"na dotik. Druge prste je treba položiti na tri tipke, ki mejijo na označene "
"tipke v srednji vrstici. Tipke za isti prst so združene glede na barvo. "
"Poskusite čim manj premikati roke in po vnosu znaka vedno poskušajte vrniti "
"prste v položaj mirovanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Start typing the text in the middle of the screen. The next key you have to "
"press is always highlighted on the keyboard visualization. While you type "
"you may make mistakes and hit the wrong key. In that case the characters "
"will displayed in red and you have to hit &Backspace; as often as necessary "
"to erase the wrongly typed characters."
msgstr ""
"Začnite tipkati besedilo na sredini zaslona. Naslednja tipka, ki jo morate "
"pritisniti, je vedno označena na vizualizaciji tipkovnice. Med tipkanjem se "
"lahko zmotite in pritisnete napačno tipko. V tem primeru bodo znaki "
"prikazani rdeče in pritisniti morate &Backspace; tako pogosto, kot je "
"potrebno, da izbrišete napačno vnesene znake."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you have successfully completed a line of text you need to press the "
"&Enter; to advance to the next line."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste uspešno dokončali vrstico besedila, morate pritisniti &Enter; za "
"napredovanje v naslednjo vrstico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The key used to advance to the next line can be changed using <link linkend="
"\"configuration_dialog\">&i18n-ktouch; configuration dialog</link>"
msgstr ""
"Ključ, ki se uporablja za napredovanje v naslednjo vrstico, lahko spremenite "
"z <link linkend=\"configuration_dialog\">&i18n-ktouch; konfiguracijsko "
"pogovorno okno</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Review your progress"
msgstr "Preglejte svoj napredek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you have completed a lesson &i18n-ktouch; will switch to the score "
"screen. It displays your current training and lesson statistics and shows a "
"graphical history of previous training sessions."
msgstr ""
"Ko zaključite lekcijo &i18n-ktouch; bo preklopil na zaslon z rezultati. "
"Prikazuje vaše trenutne statistike o usposabljanju in lekcijah ter prikazuje "
"grafično zgodovino prejšnjih vaj."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Statistics dialog of &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno s statistiko &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Statistics dialog of &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno s statistiko &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the statistics dialog you can select to show a particular lesson or "
"<guilabel>All Lessons</guilabel>. This is useful to distinguish between "
"overall performance and skill in certain lessons."
msgstr ""
"V pogovornem oknu statistike lahko izberete prikaz določene lekcije ali "
"<guilabel>Vse lekcije</guilabel>. To je koristno za razlikovanje med splošno "
"uspešnostjo in spretnostmi pri določenih lekcijah."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you feel ready for the next lesson press <guibutton>Next lesson</"
"guibutton> button in the toolbar to continue with the next lesson of the "
"current course or <guibutton>Repeat lesson</guibutton> button to try your "
"skills on the current lesson again. The <guibutton>Next lesson</guibutton> "
"button will be only available if you have passed the lesson."
msgstr ""
"Če se počutite pripravljeni na naslednjo lekcijo, pritisnite gumb "
"<guibutton>Naslednja lekcija</guibutton> v orodni vrstici, da nadaljujete z "
"naslednjo lekcijo trenutnega predmeta, ali gumb <guibutton>Ponovi lekcijo</"
"guibutton>, da preizkusite svoje sposobnosti na trenutnem tečaju spet "
"lekcija. Gumb <guibutton>Naslednja lekcija</guibutton> bo na voljo le, če "
"ste lekcijo opravili."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to switch to some other lesson or course press <guibutton>Return "
"to Home Screen</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite preklopiti na drugo lekcijo ali tečaj, pritisnite <guibutton>Nazaj "
"na začetni zaslon</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you do not want to continue the training with &i18n-ktouch; just close "
"the application window."
msgstr ""
"Če ne želite nadaljevati vadbe z &i18n-ktouch; samo zaprite okno aplikacije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "Training Preparation"
msgstr "Priprava na usposabljanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pretty much everything in the &i18n-ktouch; home screen should be self-"
"explanatory. The top toolbar is meant to be the place where you can view and "
"configure &i18n-ktouch; settings. The course selector can be used to view "
"the information about the courses and switch between them."
msgstr ""
"Skoraj vse v &i18n-ktouch; in začetni zaslon bi moral biti samoumevno. "
"Zgornja orodna vrstica je mesto, kjer si lahko ogledate in konfigurirate "
"&i18n-ktouch; nastavitve. Izbirnik tečajev lahko uporabite za ogled "
"informacij o tečajih in preklapljanje med njimi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-ktouch; toolbar"
msgstr "&i18n-ktouch; orodna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The toolbar of &i18n-ktouch; houses the profile button at the left and the "
"application menu button at the right."
msgstr ""
"Orodna vrstica &i18n-ktouch; vsebuje gumb profila na levi in gumb menija "
"aplikacij na desni."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "Profile management"
msgstr "Upravljanje profila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The profile button with the name of your profile at the left of home screen "
"toolbar can be used to manage &i18n-ktouch; profiles."
msgstr ""
"Gumb profila z imenom vašega profila na levi strani orodne vrstice začetnega "
"zaslona lahko uporabite za upravljanje &i18n-ktouch; profila."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Profile management in &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Upravljanje profila v &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Profile management in &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Upravljanje profila v &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can review the settings of the existing profiles, delete them or create "
"a new profile using <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve obstoječih profilov lahko pregledate, jih izbrišete ali ustvarite "
"nov profil z uporabo <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"gumba."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To switch to the review mode press <guibutton>Edit</guibutton>. To select a "
"profile and return to the home screen press <guibutton>Use Selected Profile "
"</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Za preklop v način pregleda pritisnite <guibutton>Uredi</guibutton>. Če "
"želite izbrati profil in se vrniti na začetni zaslon, pritisnite "
"<guibutton>Uporabi izbrani profil </guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Reviewing profile information</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pregled informacij o profilu</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Reviewing profile information</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pregled informacij o profilu</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>&i18n-ktouch; menu</title>"
msgstr "<title>&i18n-ktouch; menu</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:412
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; menu can be opened using <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> button in the toolbar of the home screen."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; meni lahko odprete z gumbom <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> v orodni vrstici začetnega zaslona."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&i18n-ktouch; menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&i18n-ktouch; meni</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&i18n-ktouch; menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&i18n-ktouch; meni</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can find a list of the menu items with their short descriptions below."
msgstr "Seznam elementov menija z njihovimi kratkimi opisi najdete spodaj."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:435
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenuitem>Full Screen Mode</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenuitem>Celozaslonski način</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Toggle</action> full screen mode of &i18n-ktouch; on and off"
msgstr ""
"<action>Preklop</action> celozaslonskega načina &i18n-ktouch; vključeno in "
"izključeno"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid "Course and Keyboard Layout Editor..."
msgstr "Urejevalnik razporeditve tečaja in tipkovnice..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:446
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Open</action> the &i18n-ktouch; <link linkend=\"extending\">editor "
"window</link>"
msgstr ""
"<action>Odpri</action> &i18n-ktouch; <link linkend=\"extending\">okno "
"urejevalnika</link>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:452
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure Typewriting Trainer..."
msgstr "Konfiguriraj program za vadbo tipkanja..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Display</action> the &i18n-ktouch; <link linkend="
"\"configuration_dialog\">configuration dialog</link>"
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaži</action> &i18n-ktouch; <link linkend=\"configuration_dialog"
"\">konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno</link>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure Shortcuts..."
msgstr "Konfiguriraj bližnjice..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Configure</action> the shortcuts you want to associate with some "
"actions"
msgstr ""
"<action>Konfigurirajte</action> bližnjice, ki jih želite povezati z "
"nekaterimi dejanji"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure Keyboard..."
msgstr "Konfiguriraj tipkovnico..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:467
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A shortcut to the &systemsettings; module to configure the keyboard "
"settings. Useful to prepare for training on a different keyboard layout."
msgstr ""
"Bližnjica do &systemsettings; modul za konfiguracijo nastavitev tipkovnice. "
"Uporabno za pripravo na usposabljanje na drugi postavitvi tipkovnice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On platforms lacking the support for detecting the keyboard layout "
"automatically, especially &Microsoft; &Windows;, this entry is replaced with "
"a submenu to select &i18n-ktouch;'s keyboard layout manually."
msgstr ""
"Na platformah, ki nimajo podpore za samodejno zaznavanje razporeditve "
"tipkovnice, zlasti &Microsoft; &Windows;, je ta vnos nadomeščen s podmenijem "
"za ročno izbiro razporeditve tipkovnice &i18n-ktouch;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu item, for "
"more information read the section about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"menus.html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; ima skupno &kde; Element menija <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za "
"več informacij preberite razdelek o <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">meniju Pomoč</ulink> programa &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration dialog"
msgstr "Konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can customize &i18n-ktouch; quite a bit. The settings apply for all "
"profiles globally. Open the configuration dialog by pressing "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button at the right of "
"the top toolbar of the home screen then choosing <guimenuitem>Configure "
"Typewriting Trainer...</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; lahko kar veliko prilagodite. Nastavitve veljajo za vse "
"profile globalno. Odprite konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno s pritiskom gumba "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> na desni strani zgornje "
"orodne vrstice začetnega zaslona nato izberite <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"vaditelja tipkanja...</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:501
#, no-c-format
msgid "Training Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve usposabljanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this dialog you can select the options that control tutor window "
"appearance and how &i18n-ktouch; behaves during training."
msgstr ""
"V tem pogovornem oknu lahko izberete možnosti, ki nadzorujejo videz okna "
"mentorja in kako &i18n-ktouch; obnaša med treningom."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:506
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Training options</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Možnosti usposabljanja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Training options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Možnosti usposabljanja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:513
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Enforce correction of typing errors</guilabel> check box can "
"be used to control whether typing errors have to be corrected."
msgstr ""
"Potrditveno polje <guilabel>Uveljavi popravljanje tipkarskih napak</"
"guilabel> lahko uporabite za nadzor, ali je treba tipkarske napake popraviti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can control the visibility of statistics and keyboard panes during "
"training using <guilabel>Show keyboard</guilabel> and <guilabel>Show real-"
"time statistics</guilabel> check boxes."
msgstr ""
"Med vadbo lahko nadzirate vidnost statistike in podokna tipkovnice s "
"potrditvenimi polji <guilabel>Prikaži tipkovnico</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Prikaži statistiko v realnem času</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:521
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The keystroke to go to the next line of training text can be chosen from two "
"options, &Enter; or &Space;."
msgstr ""
"Tipko za prehod na naslednjo vrstico besedila za usposabljanje lahko "
"izberete med dvema možnostma, &Enter; ali &Space;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:525
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Lesson unlocking limits</guilabel> can be used to choose "
"settings that control unlocking of higher level lessons. &i18n-ktouch; "
"checks the given limits at the end of each level and decides whether to "
"unlock the next lesson. If the typing speed in characters per minute and "
"correctness are <emphasis>both</emphasis> above or equal to the "
"<guilabel>Lesson unlocking limits</guilabel> &i18n-ktouch; will unlock the "
"next higher level lesson."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Omejitve odklepanja lekcije</guilabel> lahko uporabite za izbiro "
"nastavitev, ki nadzirajo odklepanje lekcij višje ravni. &i18n-ktouch; "
"preveri dane omejitve na koncu vsake stopnje in se odloči, ali bo odklenil "
"naslednjo lekcijo. Če sta hitrost tipkanja v znakih na minuto in pravilnost "
"<emphasis>oboje</emphasis> nad ali enaki <guilabel>Mejnosti odklepanja "
"lekcije</guilabel> &i18n-ktouch; bo odklenil naslednjo lekcijo višje stopnje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve barv"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:539
#, no-c-format
msgid "In this dialog you can tweak the colors used by &i18n-ktouch;."
msgstr ""
"V tem pogovornem oknu lahko nastavite barve, ki jih uporablja &i18n-ktouch;."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Color settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nastavitve barv</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Color settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nastavitve barv</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:548
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can select the background color for each finger keys."
msgstr "Za vsako prstno tipko lahko izberete barvo ozadja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid "Course and lesson selection"
msgstr "Izbira tečaja in lekcije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:559
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; automatically detects your keyboard layout and shows only the "
"courses optimized for this layout."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; samodejno zazna vašo razporeditev tipkovnice in prikaže le "
"tečaje, optimizirane za to postavitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On some platforms, especially &Windows;, keyboard layout auto-detection is "
"not available. Use the application menu to select your keyboard layout "
"manually."
msgstr ""
"Na nekaterih platformah, zlasti &Windows;, samodejno zaznavanje razporeditve "
"tipkovnice ni na voljo. Za ročno izbiro razporeditve tipkovnice uporabite "
"meni aplikacije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switching courses"
msgstr "Zamenjava tečajev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Should there are more than one course available for your keyboard layout you "
"can choose your favorite one using <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-arrow-left.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> and <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-arrow-right.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> buttons to the right of the label with course name. If "
"there is only one course the buttons won't be visible."
msgstr ""
"Če je za vašo razporeditev tipkovnice na voljo več kot en tečaj, lahko "
"izberete svojega najljubšega z uporabo <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-arrow-left.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> in <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-arrow-right.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> gumba na desni strani oznake z imenom predmeta. Če je "
"tečaj samo en, gumbi ne bodo vidni."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:582
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unlocking lessons"
msgstr "Odklepanje lekcij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:583
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have chosen <guilabel>I have no or only very little experience in "
"machine typing</guilabel> during <link linkend=\"creating_profile\">initial "
"profile creation</link> you will find that some lessons are locked. These "
"items are marked with <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-object-locked.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> icon and cannot be accessed until you pass the previous "
"lessons."
msgstr ""
"Če ste med <link linkend=\"creating_profile\">začetnim ustvarjanjem profila</"
"link> izbrali <guilabel>Nimam ali imam zelo malo izkušenj s strojnim "
"tipkanjem</guilabel>, boste ugotovili, da so nekatere lekcije zaklenjene. Ti "
"elementi so označeni z ikono <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"Icon-object-locked.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> in do njih ni mogoče dostopati, dokler ne opravite "
"prejšnjih lekcij ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:593
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The settings to pass lessons can be changed using <link linkend="
"\"configuration_dialog\">&i18n-ktouch; configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve za opravljanje lekcij lahko spremenite z <link linkend="
"\"configuration_dialog\">&i18n-ktouch; konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:600
#, no-c-format
msgid "Training on a different keyboard layout"
msgstr "Usposabljanje na drugačni postavitvi tipkovnice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With &i18n-ktouch; it is possible to use any keyboard layout for training. "
"Just press the buttons that are highlighted by the trainer, regardless to "
"the labels on your physical keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Z &i18n-ktouch; za usposabljanje je mogoče uporabiti katero koli "
"razporeditev tipkovnice. Samo pritisnite gumbe, ki jih je označil trener, ne "
"glede na oznake na vaši fizični tipkovnici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:606
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Configure Keyboard...</guimenu></menuchoice> in "
"the application menu to select a different keyboard layout. After that &i18n-"
"ktouch; will adapt accordingly and present you its courses for this layout."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Konfiguriraj tipkovnico ...</guimenu></"
"menuchoice> v meniju aplikacije, da izberete drugo razporeditev tipkovnice. "
"Po tem &i18n-ktouch; se bo ustrezno prilagodil in vam predstavil svoje "
"tečaje za to postavitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:612
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On platforms without keyboard layout auto-detection, especially &Microsoft; "
"&Windows;, you have first configure your operating system to use the layout "
"you want to train on and then select the same layout in &i18n-ktouch; via "
"the application menu."
msgstr ""
"Na platformah brez samodejnega zaznavanja razporeditve tipkovnice, zlasti "
"&Microsoft; &Windows;, morate najprej konfigurirati vaš operacijski sistem "
"za uporabo postavitve, na kateri želite trenirati, in nato izbrati isto "
"postavitev v &i18n-ktouch; prek menija aplikacije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:624
#, no-c-format
msgid "Efficient training"
msgstr "Učinkovit trening"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:626
#, no-c-format
msgid "Training techniques"
msgstr "Tehnike usposabljanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:627
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hereafter, you can find some general advice about techniques for learning "
"touch typing."
msgstr ""
"V nadaljevanju lahko najdete nekaj splošnih nasvetov o tehnikah za učenje "
"slepega tipkanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:632
#, no-c-format
msgid "Steady speed"
msgstr "Enakomerna hitrost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:633
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To be efficient when learning touch typing it is important not to simply try "
"to type as fast as possible but to keep a steady speed and find a natural "
"rhythm to press the keys."
msgstr ""
"Da bi bili pri učenju tipkanja na dotik učinkoviti, je pomembno, da ne "
"poskušate preprosto tipkati čim hitreje, temveč ohraniti enakomerno hitrost "
"in najti naraven ritem pritiskanja na tipke."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:640
#, no-c-format
msgid "Accuracy is a king"
msgstr "Natančnost je kralj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:641
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The next important thing is to focus one's attention on accuracy. Only if "
"you mastered the use of the currently unlocked keys, which means you make "
"only very few errors with them still, you will have chance in the following "
"lessons with even more keys to handle. You will notice you become almost "
"automatically master if you make only very little errors and you will save "
"precious time if you don't have to correct that many errors."
msgstr ""
"Naslednja pomembna stvar je, da se osredotočimo na natančnost. Samo če ste "
"obvladali uporabo trenutno odklenjenih tipk, kar pomeni, da z njimi delate "
"le zelo malo napak, boste imeli priložnost v naslednjih lekcijah s še več "
"tipkami, ki jih boste morali obravnavati. Opazili boste, da postanete skoraj "
"samodejno mojster, če naredite zelo malo napak, in prihranili boste "
"dragoceni čas, če vam ne bo treba popravljati toliko napak."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:650
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"That is also the reason why the default accuracy level to unlock the next "
"lesson is at 98% while the speed requirements are pretty moderate with just "
"180 characters per minute."
msgstr ""
"To je tudi razlog, zakaj je privzeta raven natančnosti za odklepanje "
"naslednje lekcije 98 %, medtem ko so zahteve glede hitrosti precej zmerne s "
"samo 180 znaki na minuto."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:657
#, no-c-format
msgid "Correcting mistakes"
msgstr "Popravljanje napak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:658
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you made mistakes it's important to correct them efficiently. Correcting "
"single characters is almost always slower than correcting the whole word. "
"For the latter you have just to press <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Backspace;</"
"keycombo>, and retype the word. The mental overhead for this is very small. "
"For the first you have to first locate the your mistake, delete precisely to "
"the location of the error, determine the missing part of the word re-type "
"it. This requires way more concentration when retyping the whole word."
msgstr ""
"Če ste naredili napake, je pomembno, da jih učinkovito popravite. "
"Popravljanje posameznih znakov je skoraj vedno počasnejše od popravljanja "
"celotne besede. Za slednje morate samo pritisniti <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Backspace;"
"</keycombo> in znova vnesti besedo. Duševni stroški za to so zelo majhni. Za "
"prvo morate najprej poiskati svojo napako, izbrisati natančno do mesta "
"napake, določiti manjkajoči del besede in jo ponovno vnesti. To zahteva "
"veliko več koncentracije pri pretipkavanju celotne besede."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:670
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pausing the training session"
msgstr "Prekinitev vadbe"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:672
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically"
msgstr "Samodejno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:673
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you open any dialog or switch to different application while you are in a "
"training session the training is paused and the timer is stopped until you "
"focus &i18n-ktouch; window again and hit any key."
msgstr ""
"Če med vadbo odprete katero koli pogovorno okno ali preklopite na drugo "
"aplikacijo, se vadba začasno ustavi in časovnik se ustavi, dokler se znova "
"ne osredotočite na okno &i18n-ktouch; in pritisnite katero koli tipko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:678
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The training session will also be paused if there will be no activity by the "
"user for five seconds."
msgstr ""
"Vadba bo prav tako začasno ustavljena, če uporabnik pet sekund ne bo izvajal "
"dejavnosti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:684
#, no-c-format
msgid "Manually"
msgstr "Ročno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:685
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can pause the current session manually using <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-media-playback-pause.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno sejo lahko ročno zaustavite z gumbom <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-media-playback-pause.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> v orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:691
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you click on <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-"
"go-home.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button in "
"the toolbar &i18n-ktouch; will pause the current session and show an overlay "
"menu with some further actions."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete gumb <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-"
"go-home.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> v orodni "
"vrstici &i18n-ktouch; bo zaustavil trenutno sejo in prikazal prekrivni meni "
"z nekaterimi nadaljnjimi dejanji."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:699
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&i18n-ktouch; menu on pausing</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&i18n-ktouch; meni ob premoru</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:703
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&i18n-ktouch; menu on pausing</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&i18n-ktouch; meni ob premoru</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tracking the learning progress"
msgstr "Sledenje učnemu napredku"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:712
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After completing a lesson, you will not return immediately to the home "
"screen. Instead a special summary and statistics screen is shown."
msgstr ""
"Po končani lekciji se ne boste takoj vrnili na začetni zaslon. Namesto tega "
"se prikaže poseben zaslon s povzetkom in statistiko."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:717
#, no-c-format
msgid "Speed and accuracy statistics"
msgstr "Statistika hitrosti in natančnosti"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:719
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Score screen progress page</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Stran z napredkom na zaslonu z rezultati</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:723
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Score screen progress page</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Stran z napredkom na zaslonu z rezultati</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:727
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filter per lesson"
msgstr "Filtriraj po lekciji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:728
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With the help of the speed and accuracy statistics page you can review your "
"learning progress and identify your weaknesses."
msgstr ""
"S pomočjo strani s statistiko hitrosti in natančnosti lahko pregledate svoj "
"učni napredek in prepoznate svoje slabosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:732
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The statistics data can be filtered by lesson using drop down box next to "
"the <guilabel>Over</guilabel> label. This feature can be useful to control "
"you progress in the current lesson and compare this progress with the "
"progress in other lessons."
msgstr ""
"Statistične podatke je mogoče filtrirati po lekciji z uporabo spustnega "
"menija poleg oznake <guilabel>Nad</guilabel>. Ta funkcija je lahko uporabna "
"za nadzor vašega napredka v trenutni lekciji in primerjavo tega napredka z "
"napredkom v drugih lekcijah."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:739
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Statistics range drop down menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Spustni meni za obseg statistik</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:743
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Statistics range drop down menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Spustni meni za obseg statistik</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:746
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additional data about the session can be viewed in overlays. If you hover "
"the mouse cursor on a point on the graph &i18n-ktouch; will show the "
"statistics of the corresponding session."
msgstr ""
"Dodatne podatke o seji si lahko ogledate v prosojnicah. Če kazalec miške "
"premaknete na točko na grafu &i18n-ktouch; bo prikazal statistiko ustrezne "
"seje."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:752
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Progress per lesson</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Napredek na lekcijo</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:756
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Progress per lesson</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Napredek na lekcijo</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid "Errors statistics"
msgstr "Statistika napak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:763
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The score screen can be switched to show errors rate for each key using drop "
"down menu next to the <guilabel>Show</guilabel> label."
msgstr ""
"Zaslon z rezultati lahko preklopite tako, da prikaže stopnjo napak za vsako "
"tipko s pomočjo spustnega menija poleg oznake <guilabel>Pokaži</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:768
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Switching the statistics mode</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Preklop načina statistike</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:772
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Switching the statistics mode</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Preklop načina statistike</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:775
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this mode, &i18n-ktouch; shows a bar diagram of errors for each key in "
"the last training session."
msgstr ""
"V tem načinu &i18n-ktouch; prikazuje stolpčni diagram napak za vsako tipko v "
"zadnjem treningu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:780
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Errors chart by the keys</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Tabela napak po tipkah</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:784
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Errors chart by the keys</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Tabela napak po tipkah</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:787
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can switch back to the lessons graph using the same drop down menu next "
"to the <guilabel>Show</guilabel> label."
msgstr ""
"Z istim spustnim menijem poleg oznake <guilabel>Pokaži</guilabel> lahko "
"preklopite nazaj na graf lekcij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:791
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have passed the lesson you may choose to start training on the next "
"lesson right away by pressing <guibutton>Next lesson</guibutton> in the "
"toolbar. Otherwise you can repeat the current lesson with <guibutton>Repeat "
"lesson</guibutton> or return to the home screen with the remaining button."
msgstr ""
"Če ste opravili lekcijo, se lahko odločite, da takoj začnete z vadbo pri "
"naslednji lekciji, tako da v orodni vrstici pritisnete <guibutton>Naslednja "
"lekcija</guibutton>. V nasprotnem primeru lahko ponovite trenutno lekcijo z "
"<guibutton>Ponovi lekcijo</guibutton> ali se vrnete na začetni zaslon s "
"preostalim gumbom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:803
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extending &i18n-ktouch;"
msgstr "Razširitev &i18n-ktouch;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:806
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating courses"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje tečajev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:807
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can easily create your own training course using the built-in &i18n-"
"ktouch; course and keyboard layout editor. Press <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button at the right of the home screen "
"toolbar then choose <guimenuitem>Course and Keyboard Layout Editor...</"
"guimenuitem>. You can choose open a course file or create an empty course "
"from scratch or using an existing course as a template."
msgstr ""
"Preprosto lahko ustvarite svoj tečaj usposabljanja z uporabo vgrajenega "
"&i18n-ktouch; urejevalnika tečaja in razporeditve tipkovnice. Pritisnite "
"gumb <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> na desni strani "
"orodne vrstice začetnega zaslona in nato izberite <guimenuitem>Tečaj in "
"tipkovnica Urejevalnik postavitve ...</guimenuitem>. Izberete lahko odprto "
"datoteko tečaja ali ustvarite prazen tečaj iz nič ali uporabite obstoječi "
"tečaj kot predlogo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:816
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You cannot edit the built-in courses, even if you have the write access to "
"the installation folder."
msgstr ""
"Vgrajenih tečajev ne morete urejati, tudi če imate dostop za pisanje v "
"namestitveno mapo."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:823
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Course and Keyboard Layout Editor main window</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Glavno okno urejevalnika tečaja in razporeditve tipkovnice</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:829
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Course and Keyboard Layout Editor main window</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Glavno okno urejevalnika tečaja in razporeditve tipkovnice</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:835
#, no-c-format
msgid "Course properties"
msgstr "Lastnosti tečaja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:836
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The course properties can be chosen using &i18n-ktouch; course creation "
"wizard. To invoke this wizard you should press <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-document-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> "
"</imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button in the toolbar of "
"<guilabel>Course and Keyboard Layout Editor</guilabel> window."
msgstr ""
"Lastnosti tečaja lahko izberete z &i18n-ktouch; čarovnik za ustvarjanje "
"tečajev. Če želite priklicati tega čarovnika, pritisnite gumb "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-document-new.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> v orodni vrstici "
"tečaja <guilabel> in okno urejevalnika razporeditve tipkovnice</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:843
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first page of creation &i18n-ktouch; wizard allows you to choose the "
"type of the data. Select <guilabel>Course</guilabel> and press "
"<guibutton>Next</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Prva stran ustvarjanja &i18n-ktouch; čarovnik omogoča izbiro vrste podatkov. "
"Izberite <guilabel>Tečaj</guilabel> in pritisnite <guibutton>Naprej</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:848 index.docbook:1228
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Choosing the type</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izbira vrste</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:854 index.docbook:1234
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Choosing the type</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izbira vrste</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:858
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The second page of wizard allows you to choose the title, the keyboard "
"layout and the description of the course."
msgstr ""
"Na drugi strani čarovnika lahko izberete naslov, razporeditev tipkovnice in "
"opis tečaja."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:863
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>New course wizard second page</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Druga stran čarovnika za nov tečaj</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:869
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>New course wizard second page</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Druga stran čarovnika za nov tečaj</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:873
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The course title is important for the quick-select menu entry in the course "
"list and for the statistics."
msgstr ""
"Naslov predmeta je pomemben za vnos menija za hitro izbiro na seznamu "
"predmetov in za statistiko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:877
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The description should be used to include information about the lesson "
"author and source of lesson data if any. This description can be shown by "
"pressing <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-dialog-"
"information.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"button in the home screen of &i18n-ktouch;."
msgstr ""
"Opis je treba uporabiti za vključitev informacij o avtorju lekcije in "
"morebitnem viru podatkov lekcije. Ta opis lahko prikažete s pritiskom gumba "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-dialog-"
"information.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> na "
"začetnem zaslonu &i18n-ktouch;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:885
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you finished with entering appropriate values press <guibutton>Next</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Ko končate z vnosom ustreznih vrednosti, pritisnite <guibutton>Naprej</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:890
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>New course wizard third page</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Tretja stran čarovnika za nov tečaj</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:896
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>New course wizard third page</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Tretja stran čarovnika za nov tečaj</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:900
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the third page of wizard you can choose an other course as a template "
"for your course. Select the course from the list and press "
"<guibutton>Finish</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"S tretjo stranjo čarovnika lahko izberete drug tečaj kot predlogo za svoj "
"tečaj. Izberite tečaj s seznama in pritisnite <guibutton>Dokončaj</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:906
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>New course editing window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Novo okno za urejanje predmeta</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:912
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>New course editing window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Novo okno za urejanje predmeta</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:916
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; will open the course editor window prepared to entering your "
"course data."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; bo odprlo okno urejevalnika tečaja, pripravljeno za vnos "
"podatkov o tečaju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:923
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding lessons"
msgstr "Dodajanje lekcij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:924
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A course is an ordered set of lessons. To be efficient for learning touch "
"typing the content of the course should meet a few requirements."
msgstr ""
"Tečaj je urejen nabor lekcij. Da bi bilo učinkovito pri učenju slepega "
"tipkanja, mora vsebina tečaja izpolnjevati nekaj zahtev."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:929
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choose a meaningful name for the lesson"
msgstr "Izberite pomenljivo ime za lekcijo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:932
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each level you can specify the new characters/keys in the lesson. It is "
"worth to include the new characters in the lesson title. Click on a name "
"label in the <guilabel>Lessons:</guilabel> list and enter some meaningful "
"name."
msgstr ""
"Za vsako raven lahko določite nove znake/ključe v lekciji. Nove znake je "
"vredno vključiti v naslov lekcije. Kliknite oznako z imenom na seznamu "
"<guilabel>Lekcije:</guilabel> in vnesite neko smiselno ime."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:938 index.docbook:956 index.docbook:976 index.docbook:994
#: index.docbook:1012 index.docbook:1032 index.docbook:1049 index.docbook:1112
#: index.docbook:1128 index.docbook:1145 index.docbook:1164
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rationale"
msgstr "Utemeljitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:939
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The text you enter as a lesson title will be shown as lesson information "
"text in the home screen course list. It will be much easier for user to "
"choose the lesson if it has a meaningful title."
msgstr ""
"Besedilo, ki ga vnesete kot naslov lekcije, bo prikazano kot besedilo "
"informacij o lekciji na seznamu tečajev na začetnem zaslonu. Uporabnik bo "
"veliko lažje izbral lekcijo, če bo imela smiseln naslov."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:946
#, no-c-format
msgid "The first lesson should cover the home keys"
msgstr "Prva lekcija bi morala pokrivati domače tipke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:949
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Usually a keyboard has two haptic markers for the keys on the second row "
"belonging to the index fingers. These two keys and the three adjacent keys "
"outwards are the home keys. That's <emphasis>asdfjkl;</emphasis> for the US "
"keyboard layout."
msgstr ""
"Običajno ima tipkovnica dva haptična označevalca za tipke v drugi vrsti, ki "
"pripadata kazalcema. Ti dve tipki in trije sosednje tipke navzven so domače "
"tipke. To je <emphasis>asdfjkl;</emphasis> za ameriško razporeditev "
"tipkovnice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:957
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Those eight keys are the start position of each finger. One must internalize "
"the location of these keys first to successfully learn touch typing."
msgstr ""
"Teh osem tipk je začetni položaj vsakega prsta. Za uspešno učenje slepega "
"tipkanja je treba najprej ponotranjiti lokacijo teh tipk."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:964
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduce two new keys per lesson"
msgstr "Predstavite dve novi tipki na lekcijo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:967
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The unlocking order of keys is not fixed, but usually keys are introduced in "
"pairs belonging to the same finger on both hands. Make your way from the "
"home keys to the ones further away. Thus, the forth row should be introduced "
"at last. Prefer keys for important characters of your language, this may "
"require to bend the introduction pattern a bit. For example in French "
"accents are really important, this warrants a lesson early-on focusing on "
"the accent key alone."
msgstr ""
"Vrstni red odklepanja tipk ni določen, vendar se običajno tipke vnesejo v "
"parih, ki pripadajo istemu prstu na obeh rokah. Pojdite od domačih tipk do "
"tistih bolj oddaljenih. Tako je treba končno uvesti četrto vrstico. Dajte "
"prednost ključem za pomembne znake vašega jezika, to bo morda zahtevalo, da "
"nekoliko upognite uvodni vzorec. Na primer, v francoščini so poudarki zelo "
"pomembni, zato je treba že na začetku lekcije osredotočiti samo na naglasni "
"ključ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:977
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If more keys are introduced the trainee might get overwhelmed by the "
"difficulty of the lesson and loose his motivation. Introduce keys for "
"important keys first to able to form real words earlier."
msgstr ""
"Če je uvedenih več tipk, bo lahko pripravnik preobremenjen zaradi težavnosti "
"lekcije in bo izgubil motivacijo. Najprej uvedite tipke za pomembne tipke, "
"da boste lahko prej oblikovali prave besede."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:986
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extra emphasis on the new keys"
msgstr "Dodaten poudarek na novih tipkah"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:989
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make sure the characters belonging to the newly introduced keys are the most "
"or at least very frequently used characters in the lesson text."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da so znaki, ki pripadajo novo uvedenim tipkam, najpogosteje "
"ali vsaj zelo pogosto uporabljeni znaki v besedilu lekcije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:995
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the trainee passes a lesson he should have mastered the new keys. This is "
"only possible if the lesson contains a significant amount of the new "
"characters."
msgstr ""
"Če pripravnik opravi lekcijo, bi moral obvladati nove tipke. To je mogoče "
"le, če lekcija vsebuje precejšnjo količino novih znakov."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:1003
#, no-c-format
msgid "Intersperse lessons with new keys with repetition lessons"
msgstr "Prepletajte lekcije z novimi tipkami z lekcijami ponavljanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1006
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every two to three lessons add a repetition lesson without any new keys. "
"These should have an even character mix covering all already introduced "
"characters."
msgstr ""
"Vsaki dve do tri lekcije dodajte lekcijo ponavljanja brez novih tipk. Ti "
"morajo imeti enakomerno mešanico znakov, ki zajema vse že predstavljene "
"znake."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1013
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Such lessons help to strengthen the acquired skills and provide a way to "
"check the overall training level. They are also better suited for repeated "
"training to further improve one's general typing skills."
msgstr ""
"Takšne lekcije pomagajo krepiti pridobljene veščine in omogočajo preverjanje "
"splošne ravni usposabljanja. Primernejši so tudi za ponavljajoče se "
"usposabljanje za nadaljnje izboljšanje splošnih veščin tipkanja."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:1022
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dedicated lessons for capitalization"
msgstr "Namenske lekcije za velike začetnice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1025
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There should be several lessons focusing sorely on capitalization. Ideally "
"capitalization is introduced in multiple steps: At first only the left "
"&Shift; key, then the right, then both and followed by one or more "
"repetition lessons."
msgstr ""
"Obstajati mora več lekcij, ki se osredotočajo izključno na uporabo velikih "
"začetnic. V idealnem primeru se uporaba velikih začetnic uvede v več "
"korakih: najprej le levi &Shift; tipko, nato desno, nato obe in sledi ena "
"ali več lekcij ponavljanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1033
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mastering capitalization is the most difficult part of learning touch "
"typing. Therefore extra effort must be spend on these lessons."
msgstr ""
"Obvladovanje velikih začetnic je najtežji del učenja tipkanja na dotik. Zato "
"je treba v te lekcije vložiti dodaten trud."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:1041
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cover the complete keyboard layout"
msgstr "Pokrijte celotno postavitev tipkovnice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1044
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This includes characters and symbols accessible via other modifiers than "
"&Shift;. Ideally every character, number and symbol which is printed on a "
"real keyboard should be covered."
msgstr ""
"To vključuje znake in simbole, ki so dostopni prek drugih modifikatorjev kot "
"&Shift;. V idealnem primeru bi morali biti zajeti vsi znaki, številke in "
"simboli, ki so natisnjeni na pravi tipkovnici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1050
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The more complete a course is the more the trainee can learn from it. It "
"also keeps the course interesting for already advanced typists."
msgstr ""
"Bolj ko je tečaj popoln, več se lahko tečajnik iz njega nauči. Prav tako "
"ohranja tečaj zanimiv za že napredne strojepisce."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1059
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button to add new "
"lesson to the course, <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-list-remove.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> button to remove selected lesson from your course and "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-arrow-up.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>/<inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-arrow-down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> buttons to rearrange the lessons in the "
"course."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite gumb <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-"
"list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>, da v "
"tečaj dodate novo lekcijo, <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"Icon-list-remove.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> gumb za odstranitev izbrane lekcije iz tečaja in "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon- arrow-up.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>/<inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-arrow-down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> gumbi za prerazporeditev lekcij v tečaju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1074
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Delete lessons only with caution. Doing so may reset the unlocking progress "
"of the users of the course. If you are planning to revise a course "
"thoroughly it is usually better to use the existing course as a base for a "
"new one."
msgstr ""
"Lekcije izbrišite le previdno. S tem lahko ponastavite napredek pri "
"odklepanju uporabnikov tečaja. Če nameravate tečaj temeljito prenoviti, je "
"običajno bolje uporabiti obstoječi tečaj kot osnovo za novega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1080
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The content of the lesson can be edited using bottom right edit field. You "
"can copy snippets of the text from your favorite text editor and paste them "
"to this field."
msgstr ""
"Vsebino lekcije lahko urejate v spodnjem desnem polju za urejanje. Delčke "
"besedila lahko kopirate iz svojega najljubšega urejevalnika besedil in jih "
"prilepite v to polje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1085
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-document-"
"open.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button to "
"open a generic text file that will be loaded into the lesson text field."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite gumb <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-"
"document-open.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>, da "
"odprete generično besedilno datoteko, ki bo naložena v lekcijo besedilno "
"polje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1091
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-format-"
"justify-fill.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"button can be used to wrap the lesson text. &i18n-ktouch; editor wraps text "
"such that every line of the lesson does not exceed the recommended 60 "
"characters limit."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-format-"
"justify-fill.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"lahko uporabite za prelom besedila lekcije. &i18n-ktouch; urejevalnik "
"prelomi besedilo tako, da vsaka vrstica lekcije ne preseže priporočene "
"omejitve 60 znakov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1098
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let's assume you want to add a new lesson. There are a few guidelines you "
"may want to consider:"
msgstr ""
"Recimo, da želite dodati novo lekcijo. Morda boste želeli upoštevati nekaj "
"smernic:"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:1104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Give lessons a descriptive title"
msgstr "Lekcijam dajte opisni naslov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Name the new characters if there are any or otherwise state what the lesson "
"is about."
msgstr ""
"Poimenujte nove like, če obstajajo, ali drugače povejte, o čem govori "
"lekcija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Good titles make it easier to find the right course if one wants to train on "
"something specific."
msgstr ""
"Dobri naslovi olajšajo iskanje pravega tečaja, če se želimo usposabljati na "
"nečem specifičnem."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:1120
#, no-c-format
msgid "The lesson text should be composed out of real words and sentences"
msgstr "Besedilo lekcije naj bo sestavljeno iz pravih besed in stavkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Optimally a lesson forms a comprehensible contiguous text on a freely chosen "
"subject."
msgstr ""
"Optimalno lekcija tvori razumljivo sosednje besedilo na prosto izbrano temo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Training with real words and sentences is more effective than with arbitrary "
"random character combinations since that is closer to real typing. And it is "
"more fun."
msgstr ""
"Usposabljanje s pravimi besedami in stavki je učinkovitejše kot s poljubnimi "
"naključnimi kombinacijami znakov, saj je to bližje pravemu tipkanju. In bolj "
"zabavno je."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:1136
#, no-c-format
msgid "Avoid non-word character combinations"
msgstr "Izogibajte se nebesednim kombinacijam znakov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This may impossible in the very first lessons where only a few characters "
"are available, but as soon as possible only real words should be used. Never "
"use misspelled words."
msgstr ""
"To je morda nemogoče v prvih učnih urah, kjer je na voljo le nekaj znakov, "
"vendar je treba čim prej uporabiti samo prave besede. Nikoli ne uporabljajte "
"napačno črkovanih besed."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Random character combinations are hard to type and are seldom found in day-"
"to-day typing. Misspelled words on the other hand are confusing and have "
"even a negative learning value, since the trainee may memorize the wrong "
"spelling."
msgstr ""
"Naključne kombinacije znakov je težko tipkati in jih redko najdemo pri "
"vsakodnevnem tipkanju. Napačno črkovane besede pa povzročajo zmedo in imajo "
"celo negativno učno vrednost, saj si lahko praktikant zapomni napačno "
"črkovanje."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:1155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lesson text should be roughly 600 characters long"
msgstr "Besedilo lekcije naj bo dolgo približno 600 znakov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"They may be longer, up to 1200 characters is okay, but shorter lessons "
"should be avoided. This is especially true for repetition lessons."
msgstr ""
"Lahko so daljše, do 1200 znakov je v redu, vendar se je treba izogibati "
"krajšim lekcijam. To še posebej velja za ponavljalni pouk."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keeping within this range ensures that a untrained typist (~120 characters "
"per minute) can finish a lesson in five to ten minutes. Longer lessons get "
"frustrating, shorter ones are ineffective."
msgstr ""
"Ohranjanje znotraj tega razpona zagotavlja, da lahko neizkušen strojepisec "
"(~120 znakov na minuto) zaključi lekcijo v petih do desetih minutah. Daljše "
"lekcije postanejo frustrirajoče, krajše so neučinkovite."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quality checks in the lesson text editor"
msgstr "Preverjanje kakovosti v urejevalniku besedil lekcije"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1178
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Quality check in the course editing window</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Preverjanje kakovosti v oknu za urejanje tečaja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1184
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Quality check in the course editing window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Preverjanje kakovosti v oknu za urejanje tečaja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Above is a screenshot of the course editor with one of a problematic lesson "
"loaded showing one of the built-in quality-assurance checks: if a lesson "
"contains characters not available in that lesson, because they are not among "
"the configured new characters of this lesson or any previous one, they are "
"highlighted in red. There is also a check for too long lines resulting in a "
"muted color for the characters behind the allowed column."
msgstr ""
"Zgoraj je posnetek zaslona urejevalnika tečaja z eno od naloženih "
"problematičnih lekcij, ki prikazuje eno od vgrajenih preverjanj "
"zagotavljanja kakovosti: če lekcija vsebuje znake, ki v tej lekciji niso na "
"voljo, ker niso med konfiguriranimi novimi znaki te lekcije ali katerega "
"koli prejšnjega, so označeni z rdečo. Na voljo je tudi preverjanje predolgih "
"vrstic, kar ima za posledico utišano barvo znakov za dovoljenim stolpcem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left side there is a list over all data files &i18n-ktouch; knows "
"about, built-in and user-created alike. If the user selects a built-in "
"resource the editor will degrade to a simple viewer, though. If the user "
"selects a keyboard layout the program will adapt appropriately."
msgstr ""
"Na levi strani je seznam vseh podatkovnih datotek &i18n-ktouch; ve o, "
"vgrajenih in uporabniško ustvarjenih. Če uporabnik izbere vgrajeni vir, se "
"bo urejevalnik spremenil v preprost pregledovalnik. Če uporabnik izbere "
"razporeditev tipkovnice, se program ustrezno prilagodi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1207
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating keyboard layouts"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje postavitev tipkovnice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can create your own keyboard layouts using built-in &i18n-ktouch; "
"editor. Usually it's best is to start with an existing layout close to the "
"keyboard layout you want to create, and use that as a base for own layout. "
"That way you can avoid a lot of work."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite lahko lastne postavitve tipkovnice z uporabo vgrajenega &i18n-"
"ktouch; urejevalnika. Običajno je najbolje, da začnete z obstoječo "
"postavitvijo, ki je blizu postavitvi tipkovnice, ki jo želite ustvariti, in "
"jo uporabite kot osnovo za lastno postavitev. Tako se lahko izognete preveč "
"dela."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1214
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyboard layout properties"
msgstr "Lastnosti postavitve tipkovnice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The keyboard layout properties can be chosen using &i18n-ktouch; keyboard "
"layout creation wizard. To invoke this wizard you should press "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-document-new.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button in the "
"toolbar of <guilabel>Course and Keyboard Layout Editor</guilabel> window."
msgstr ""
"Lastnosti razporeditve tipkovnice lahko izberete z &i18n-ktouch; čarovnik za "
"ustvarjanje postavitve tipkovnice. Če želite priklicati tega čarovnika, "
"pritisnite gumb <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-"
"document-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> v "
"orodni vrstici tečaja <guilabel> in okno urejevalnika razporeditve "
"tipkovnice</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first page of creation &i18n-ktouch; wizard allows you to choose the "
"type of the data. Select <guilabel>Keyboard layout</guilabel> and press "
"<guibutton>Next</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Prva stran ustvarjanja &i18n-ktouch; čarovnik omogoča izbiro vrste podatkov. "
"Izberite <guilabel>Razporeditev tipkovnice</guilabel> in pritisnite "
"<guibutton>Naprej</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The second page of wizard allows you to choose the title and the name of the "
"layout."
msgstr "Na drugi strani čarovnika lahko izberete naslov in ime postavitve."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1243
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>New layout wizard second page</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nova druga stran čarovnika za postavitev</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1249
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>New layout wizard second page</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Druga stran čarovnika za novo postavitev</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The layout title is important for the quick-select menu entry in the layout "
"list of <link linkend=\"ktouch_menu\">&i18n-ktouch; configuration menu</"
"link> and for the statistics."
msgstr ""
"Naslov postavitve je pomemben za vnos menija za hitro izbiro na seznamu "
"postavitev <link linkend=\"ktouch_menu\">&i18n-ktouch; konfiguracijski meni</"
"link> in za statistiko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The layout name will be used as a name of the layout by &i18n-ktouch; "
"internally."
msgstr "Ime postavitve bo &i18n-ktouch; uporabil kot ime postavitve interno."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1262
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>New layout wizard third page</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Tretja stran čarovnika za novo postavitev</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1268
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>New layout wizard third page</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Tretja stran čarovnika za novo postavitev</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the third page of wizard you can choose other layout as a template for "
"your layout. Select the course from the list and press <guibutton>Finish</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"S tretjo stranjo čarovnika lahko izberete drugo postavitev kot predlogo za "
"vašo postavitev. Izberite tečaj s seznama in pritisnite <guibutton>Dokončaj</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1278
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>New layout editing window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Novo okno za urejanje postavitve</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1284
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>New layout editing window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Novo okno za urejanje postavitve</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; will open the editor window prepared to entering your keyboard "
"layout data."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; bo odprlo okno urejevalnika, pripravljeno za vnos podatkov o "
"vaši postavitvi tipkovnice."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1295
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding keys"
msgstr "Dodajanje tipk"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> <guilabel>Normal "
"Key</guilabel> button to add new normal key or <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> <guilabel>Special Key</guilabel> button to "
"add new special key (modifier keys, &Space;, &Backspace;, &Tab;, "
"<keycap>Caps Lock</keycap> or &Enter;) to the layout. The "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-edit-delete.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject><guilabel>Delete</"
"guilabel> button can be used to remove a selected key from your layout. The "
"scale can be changed using the slider at the right part of the editor "
"toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite gumb <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-"
"list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"<guilabel>Normalna tipka</guilabel>, da dodate novo običajno tipko ali gumb "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-add.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> <guilabel>Posebna "
"tipka</guilabel> za dodajanje nove posebne tipke (modifikacijske tipke, "
"&Space;, &Backspace;, &Tab;, <keycap>Caps Lock</keycap> ali &Enter;) na "
"postavitev. Z gumbom <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-edit-delete.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject><guilabel>Izbriši</guilabel> lahko uporabite za "
"odstranitev izbrane tipke iz vaše postavitve. Merilo lahko spremenite z "
"drsnikom na desnem delu orodne vrstice urejevalnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The properties of individual keys can be edited using the bottom pane of the "
"editor window."
msgstr ""
"Lastnosti posameznih tipk lahko urejate v spodnjem podoknu okna urejevalnika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1316
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal keys"
msgstr "Navadne tipke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1317
#, no-c-format
msgid "It is easy to change the size or properties of a key."
msgstr "Velikost ali lastnosti tipke je enostavno spremeniti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Begin by clicking on the key you want to change. This selects the clicked "
"key as the current key."
msgstr ""
"Začnite s klikom na ključ, ki ga želite spremeniti. To izbere kliknjeno "
"tipko kot trenutno tipko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are now 4 squares on the corners of the key. By dragging these "
"squares, you will be able to drag the key border to a new location. Dragging "
"the whole key allows you to change the key position in the layout."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj so na vogalih ključa 4 polja. Če povlečete te kvadrate, boste lahko "
"potegnili obrobo ključa na novo lokacijo. Če povlečete celotno tipko, lahko "
"spremenite položaj tipke v postavitvi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The numerical characteristics of the key geometry can also be changed using "
"the <guilabel>Geometry</guilabel> section of the pane at the bottom of the "
"editor window."
msgstr ""
"Numerične značilnosti geometrije ključa lahko spremenite tudi z uporabo "
"razdelka <guilabel>Geometrija</guilabel> v podoknu na dnu okna urejevalnika."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1335
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Editing an individual key properties</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Urejanje lastnosti posamezne tipke</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1341
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Editing an individual key properties</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Urejanje lastnosti posamezne tipke</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The bottom pane can also be used to choose finger to press the key and "
"switch the haptic marker for the key."
msgstr ""
"Spodnje podokno lahko uporabite tudi za izbiro prsta za pritisk na tipko in "
"preklop haptičnega označevalca za tipko."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1350
#, no-c-format
msgid "Key characters"
msgstr "Ključni liki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The characters that will be shown on a key can be changed using the "
"<guilabel> Characters</guilabel> section of the editor bottom pane."
msgstr ""
"Znake, ki bodo prikazani na tipki, lahko spremenite v razdelku <guilabel> "
"Znaki</guilabel> v spodnjem podoknu urejevalnika."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1356
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Editing the character position</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Urejanje položaja znaka</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1362
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Editing the character position</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Urejanje položaja znaka</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add a character by pressing <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> button. A selected character can be removed by pressing "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-remove.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button."
msgstr ""
"Znak lahko dodate tako, da pritisnete gumb <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>. Izbrani znak lahko odstranite s pritiskom na gumb "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-remove.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also select the position of individual characters on the key by "
"double-clicking in the <guilabel>Position</guilabel> column."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko tudi položaj posameznih znakov na tipki z dvoklikom v stolpcu "
"<guilabel>Položaj</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1381
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifiers"
msgstr "Modifikatorji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are several modifier keys that can be defined in &i18n-ktouch;. They "
"can be edited as normal keys but it is helpful to know identifier of "
"modifier key to use them as appropriate. The table of modifier keys "
"identifiers is given below."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja več modifikacijskih tipk, ki jih je mogoče definirati v &i18n-"
"ktouch;. Urejate jih lahko kot običajne ključe, vendar je koristno poznati "
"identifikator modifikacijskega ključa, da jih boste ustrezno uporabili. "
"Spodaj je podana tabela identifikatorjev modifikacijskih ključev."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1388
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifier keys"
msgstr "Modifikacijske tipke"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1392
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifier key"
msgstr "Tipka za spreminjanje"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1393
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifier id in &i18n-ktouch;"
msgstr "ID modifikatorja v &i18n-ktouch;"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1398
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Alt;"
msgstr "&Alt;"

