msgstr "<literal>left_shift</literal> ali <literal>desni_shift</literal>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1413
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom Lessons"
msgstr "Lekcije po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The custom lessons feature allows you to extend your training material in an "
"easy way by choosing some arbitrary text."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija lekcije po meri vam omogoča, da na enostaven način razširite "
"gradivo za usposabljanje z izbiro poljubnega besedila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The custom lessons are gathered in a special course, the <guilabel>Custom "
"Lessons</guilabel> course, always available right next to <link linkend="
"\"picking_a_lesson\">the normal built-in courses</link>."
msgstr ""
"Lekcije po meri so zbrane v posebnem tečaju, tečaju <guilabel>Lekcije po "
"meri</guilabel>, ki je vedno na voljo poleg <link linkend=\"picking_a_lesson"
"\">običajnih vgrajenih tečajev</link>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1424
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Custom lessons course</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Tečaj lekcije po meri</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1430
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Custom lessons course</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Tečaj lekcije po meri</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This special course mostly acts like any other, training and statistics "
"gathering works as usual. Clicking on <guibutton>Add New Lesson</guibutton> "
"or the <guibutton>Edit</guibutton> button (the pencil icon for existing "
"lessons) brings up a stripped-down version of <link linkend=\"adding_lessons"
"\">the normal lesson editor</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ta posebni tečaj večinoma deluje kot vsak drug, usposabljanje in zbiranje "
"statistike poteka kot običajno. S klikom na <guibutton>Dodaj novo lekcijo</"
"guibutton> ali gumb <guibutton>Uredi</guibutton> (ikona svinčnika za "
"obstoječe lekcije) se prikaže skrajšana različica <link linkend="
"\"adding_lessons\">običajne lekcije urejevalnik</link>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1442
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Custom lesson editor</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Urejevalnik lekcij po meri</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1448
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Custom lesson editor</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Urejevalnik lekcij po meri</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1452
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The editor will highlight problematic sections of your lesson texts. "
"Characters which can't by typed on your keyboard layout will be shown on a "
"dark red background, lines which are considered to be too long use a pink "
"background for the excess characters. &i18n-ktouch; requires that every line "
"of the lesson does not exceed the recommended 60 characters limit."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik bo osvetlil problematične dele vaših učnih besedil. Znaki, ki "
"jih ne morete vnesti na vaši razporeditvi tipkovnice, bodo prikazani na "
"temno rdečem ozadju, vrstice, za katere se šteje, da so predolge, "
"uporabljajo rožnato ozadje za odvečne znake. &i18n-ktouch; zahteva, da vsaka "
"vrstica lekcije ne presega priporočene omejitve 60 znakov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1456
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guibutton>Done</guibutton> button to confirm your edits or close "
"the editor window to cancel them."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite gumb <guibutton>Končano</guibutton>, da potrdite svoja urejanja "
"ali zaprete okno urejevalnika, da jih prekličete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1460
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All custom lessons are stored per profile and keyboard layout individually. "
"Use this to manage different sets of lessons depending on the specific "
"training situation."
msgstr ""
"Vse lekcije po meri so shranjene za profil in postavitev tipkovnice posebej. "
"Uporabite to za upravljanje različnih sklopov lekcij, odvisno od specifične "
"situacije usposabljanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1467
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sharing your results"
msgstr "Delite svoje rezultate"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to save your courses and keyboard layouts in separate files "
"outside of the local &i18n-ktouch; database."
msgstr ""
"Svoje tečaje in razporeditve tipkovnice lahko shranite v ločene datoteke "
"zunaj lokalnega &i18n-ktouch; zbirka podatkov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1473
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export/Import"
msgstr "Izvoz/uvoz"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1474
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To export a course or keyboard layout in a separate file choose the "
"corresponding item in the list at the left part of <guilabel>Course and "
"Keyboard Layout Editor</guilabel> window and press <guibutton>Export</"
"guibutton> button in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvoziti tečaj ali razporeditev tipkovnice v ločeni datoteki, "
"izberite ustrezen element na seznamu v levem delu okna <guilabel>Urejevalnik "
"tečaja in razporeditve tipkovnice</guilabel> in pritisnite gumb "
"<guibutton>Izvozi</guibutton> v orodni vrstici ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; will open a standard &kde; save dialog. Description of this "
"dialog in details can be found in the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/files."
"html\">Opening and Saving Files</ulink> chapter of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; bo odprl standardni &kde; pogovorno okno za shranjevanje. "
"Podrobnejši opis tega pogovornega okna je na voljo v poglavju <ulink url="
"\"help:/fundamentals/files.html\">Odpiranje in shranjevanje datotek</ulink> "
"v &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1484
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can choose the name and the location of the &XML; file to be saved."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko ime in lokacijo datoteke &XML; datoteko, ki jo želite "
"shraniti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1487
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you find it worth to share your files with over users, please send them "
"with some description to <ulink url=\"mailto:kde-edu@kde.org\">kde-edu "
"mailing list</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Če se vam zdi vredno deliti svoje datoteke z več uporabniki, jih pošljite z "
"opisom na <ulink url=\"mailto:kde-edu@kde.org\">poštni seznam kde-edu</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1493
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your data should be licensed under <ulink url=\"https://www.gnu.org/licenses/"
"gpl-2.0.html\">&GNU; General Public License, version 2</ulink> to include "
"them into the default &i18n-ktouch; installation."
msgstr ""
"Vaši podatki morajo biti licencirani pod <ulink url=\"https://www.gnu.org/"
"licenses/gpl-2.0.html\">&GNU; Splošna javna licenca, različica 2</ulink>, da "
"jih vključite v privzeto &i18n-ktouch; namestitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To import your data files into &i18n-ktouch; press <guibutton>Import</"
"guibutton> button in the toolbar and choose &XML; file that was earlier "
"exported using &i18n-ktouch;."
msgstr ""
"Za uvoz podatkovnih datotek v &i18n-ktouch; pritisnite gumb "
"<guibutton>Uvozi</guibutton> v orodni vrstici in izberite &XML; datoteko, ki "
"je bila prej izvožena z &i18n-ktouch;."

